  "title": "[ENTRY-LVL] Marketing & Brand Ambassador (training provided)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Company Overview</strong></p><p>We are a growing organization specializing in live campaigns, events, and brand activations. We focus on developing talent through hands-on experience, structured training, and clear career progression.</p><p><br /><strong>Job Description</strong></p><p>As a Brand Ambassador, you will represent client brands, engage with the public, and support marketing campaigns and events. This role provides practical experience in communication, customer engagement, and marketing fundamentals.</p><p></p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><p>* Represent client brands professionally at events and campaigns</p><p>* Engage with customers to create positive and memorable experiences</p><p>* Assist in executing marketing campaigns and brand activations</p><p>* Work with team members to achieve campaign goals</p><p>* Learn marketing, communication, and customer engagement skills</p><p></p><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><p>* Interest in marketing, events, or customer engagement</p><p>* Positive attitude and eagerness to learn</p><p>* Good communication and interpersonal skills</p><p>* Team player and proactive approach</p><p>* No experience required; full training provided</p><p></p><p><strong>What We Offer</strong></p><p>* Structured training and mentorship</p><p>* Hands-on marketing and events experience</p><p>* Performance-based career progression</p><p>* Incentives, rewards, and exposure to live campaigns</p><p>* Supportive and collaborative team culture</p><p></p>",
